            },
            {
                "s2_paper_id": "bfb8a187d90f286998d8c2b98c4546efb20fa675",
                "title": "Application of intelligent control technology in aero-generator's overload protection",
                "year": 2020,
                "venue": "2020 IEEE International Conference on Information Technology,Big Data and Artificial Intelligence (ICIBA)",
                "citation_count": 1,
                "reference_count": 7,
                "abstract": "When the aero-generator is overloaded, the power distribution system will carry out overload protection control. The overload protection action time is one important parameter. If the action time is too long, the aero-generator may be burnt down; on the other hand, if the action time is too short, it is easy to cause the electrical power supply fluctuation and reduce the power supply quality. Therefore, in order to effectively realize the overload protection control of aero-generator, the key problem is how to determine the best action time. In this paper, an intelligent control (fuzzy control) method will be used to determine the optimal overload protection action time to improve the power supply quality and prolong the service life of the aero-generator, which makes the overload protection control more intelligent and advanced for the electrical power supply system.",
